 Enyimba will host South Africa’s TS Galaxy in the CAF Confederation Cup…on Sunday.<br />  Enyimba will take on the South African side at the Enyimba International Stadium on Sunday, with the return leg coming up days later in South Africa.
 
While in their Ota camp, the team played a 1-1 draw with fellow NPFL side MFM FC.
 
The Usman Abdallah’s side arrived in Aba on Tuesday and the club media manager, Zazi Bariza confirmed that the team is in perfect shape for the clash.
 
